{"tid":1647152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業發佈-紅媒追擊師","createTime":"2019-10-11T15:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:53:41.000Z","uid":186399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"402a95f1da5be6aa8766cf353dd1a1253f9225b5","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:32:48.000Z","msg":"手足們，場仗一定要繼續打落去，唔可以比失去咗既手足白白犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n六月以來媒體戰就一直從來都沒停過，CCTVB哩類垃圾紅媒一直係我地媒體戰線上既最大敵人。可能有人唔認同，但係我的確識唔少到而加仲係唔點留意時事既真中立存在。當佢地唔了解事情來龍去脈既時候，<span style=\"color: red;\">係好容易受傳媒剪輯後既速食新聞同埋紅媒既選擇性報道影響，所以追擊佢地係有必要性。</span><br />\n<br />\n由於我沒睇CCTVB好耐，但係見到隔離抵制<span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB post有講而加CCTVB幾乎得番中資公司既廣告，可想而知佢地既自我番查係只會愈來愈勁。</span> 而其他紅到發黑既媒體更加唔駛講，一定會小心選擇新聞畫面。<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望手足係之後既十八區開花同埋其他示威活動，<span style=\"color: red;\">搵人跟實班紅媒，用會比佢地自我審查既圖跟實佢個鏡頭等佢影埋</span>，例如用一啲侮辱維尼既圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbZVAG5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbZVAG5.png&h=f3513896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eUj2Z8L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeUj2Z8L.jpg&h=beeb04a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePXHfG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePXHfG6.jpg&h=271ef6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPOLdtN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPOLdtN.jpg&h=fca5943f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7Mdnm8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7Mdnm8.jpg&h=dafd0f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ys8LdtP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYs8LdtP.jpg&h=35cf9e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yofxCVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyofxCVv.jpg&h=a57091a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(ps:唔好用文字啦，一般一個新聞畫面最多得個5-6秒，佢照播都沒咩問題，因為沒咩人會慢慢係到睇字。)<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做可以等佢地慢慢自我審查，自己決定播唔播。<br />\n除咗可以追擊班紅媒，一來可以防止班撚樣影大頭保護手足，二來比起屌尻或姐攻擊班紅媒咁樣做會較為合適，畢竟新聞自由係我地口口聲聲話要捍衛既嘢。<br />\n同埋無論大家承唔承認都好，運動持續咗四個月，<span style=\"color: red;\">其實五大訴求跟本沒人在意，而加事實上就係東西方核心價值既對壘。</span>外國人wfc你香港人有沒達成五大訴求，而加係<span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨直接威脅到美國人既生活所以佢地先支持香港，所以fuck the ccp比起五大訴求一定更加吸引國際眼光。</span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"2db81308bbac85acb557e203eeb16807c12579be","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cc53a53352fa47dae5d8bbf45192726fb57eba7","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb5f14ab166a2c875c395781d6378d3b1adf00ff","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3bd0b0eb9783b0e121ba144f688b014cedc669","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a4ee98b6727a5b4cd931fb9f77415977432b1eee","tid":1647152,"uid":186399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:36:19.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"26f16745aaf02d263f10231477027bce3a3d5bc5","tid":1647152,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:36:37.000Z","msg":"佢地會唔會連個人都p走埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d42e50486ad11cd6549da0ab59b7f8f5a30bc50","tid":1647152,"